title: This Week in Warhammer – The Solar Auxilia March to War
description:
Reinforcements are on their way for Kingdoms of Bretonnia and Tomb Kings of Khemri armies in Warhammer: The Old World. 

Plus there's new Solar Auxilia and Space Marines miniatures for Warhammer: The Horus Heresy. 

Get the lowdown on next week's pre-orders: https://ow.ly/u75250QH6ae
